Summary
I am a 3d artist, Generalist. In my studio I work on the creation of photorealistic 3d models, scenery and scenes, architectural design, visual design for festivals and concerts.

I am engaged in visual development and search of design solutions for different kinds of projects. I am interested in all areas of computer graphics, but my favorite areas are photorealistic modeling, compositing, lookdev and rendering.

Among the projects, companies, and clients I've had the pleasure of working with Warby Parker, Alexander McQueen, AMD, Hermes, Crocus City Hall, Circle of light, Museum of the Ministry of Emergency Situations of Russia, Aeroflot, Ray Ban, Valio, HTC
